title: Cattle predation spelled demise of grizzly sow
text:
Published By: Billings Gazette: Outdoors - Today 
Elusive, resourceful and in the end a troublemaker, grizzly bear 882 was killed Oct. 1 for developing an intolerable appetite for cattle....
